Package com.project.CyShare.app

Class User

java.lang.Object
com.project.CyShare.app.User
@Entity public class User extends Object
User entity class. Holds id number, userName, password, full name, and is linked to a car object and location.
Author:
Hugo Alvarez Valdivia
